# File containing details of test specifications for
# specific simulations that reference keys defined in
# tests/tests.toml files defined in the simulation 
# directories
#
# Comments can be added using a `#` sign and individual
# tests spec can be defined with relevant options as shown below
#
# List of options
# --test, -t (string value), desired test key/node from tests/tests.toml
# --nprocs, -np (integer value), number of procs to be used
# --nthreads, -nt (integer value), number of threads to be used
# --env, -e (colon seperated environment variables)
# --debug (boolean), to run test in debug
# --cbase, -cb (date string YYYY-MM-DD[_version])
# --rbase, -rb (date string YYYY-MM-DD[_version])

# Incompressible Navier-Stokes UniTests
incompFlow/RisingBubble --test=UnitTest/RisingBubble/AMReX/2d --nprocs=4
incompFlow/LidDrivenCavity --test=UnitTest/LidDrivenCavity/AMReX/2d --debug

